cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on enabling robotic grasping through shape completion using a 3D CNN. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper involves processing 2.5D pointclouds and using a CNN for shape completion. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a neural network on a large dataset of 3D exemplars. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves using a machine learning approach to enable robotic grasping. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves generating completed 3D mesh models for grasping.
